Music Video list:
01. Therion - Birth Of Venus Illegitima

09. Nightwish - The Carpenter
10. The Gathering - Eleanor (Live In Poland)

Some editions contain an extra video:
14. Darkside - The Gloaming
All the videos are good, one of the best I have seen. A must have!
